{"tid":411084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國皇家空軍搭香港航空","createTime":"2017-09-23T13:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T14:57:15.000Z","uid":69930,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab92c7ad130dd8414c7a6a4a47e7c217d623c8e0","tid":411084,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"前英國皇家空軍機師: 一定唔坐香港航空<br />\n<br />\n前英國皇家空軍機師， 喺因航做左21 年，<br />\n個機師過檔香港航空，之後頂唔順辭咗職，話擔心香港航空安全問題， <br />\n重話一定唔坐香港航空<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;worryingly poor standards among the pilots he tested and his general concern over safety issues at the seven-year-old airline&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I wouldn't put my wife and kids on Hong Kong Airlines - I really wouldn't,&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1287104/safety-questioned-hong-kong-airlines\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Farticle%2F1287104%2Fsafety-questioned-hong-kong-airlines&d=JKh%2BUJ3vdBTNOyz78cyjaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=60a6160e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1287104/safety-questioned-hong-kong-airlines</a>"},{"pid":"552e1c211f6542cf354993eed198ca94f0006cae","tid":411084,"uid":6604,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"香港航空<br />\n很支那 唔香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d9d57af3094e68a16ee91d75584adcbf78be25","tid":411084,"uid":79563,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港航空<br />\n很支那 唔香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港航空<br />\n很支那  <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>扮</strong></span>香港"},{"pid":"aceb1410b5dbdabafb61d6f71826d2e43a4812ee","tid":411084,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"Be lenient on him because he doesn't fly a lot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大陸化<br />\n<br />\n香港航空? 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734f509a862fe4dc6fe547f78676048bcf53c7ee","tid":411084,"uid":128014,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"近年好撚多中資掛羊頭賣狗肉<br />\n<br />\n交通：香港航空，香港快運<br />\n<br />\n媒體：香港01 ，創辦人于品海<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他例子？"},{"pid":"ec4c3e2778dc3218f092eadc13c38ee9b80f701b","tid":411084,"uid":69930,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;<br />\n中資公司香港航空一名空少，<br />\n早前要求一名醉酒乘客下機，但乘客疑為公司高層的友好，<br />\n該名空少其後遭解僱，港航被指秋後算帳。<br />\n前線員工不滿管理層懲罰堅守安全規例的同事，漠視機艙安全；<br />\n港航並無正面回應為何解僱涉事員工。<br />\n&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170923/57245586[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170923%2F57245586%5B%2Furl%5D&d=JKh%2BUJ3vdBTNOyz78cyjaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=54ca2fdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170923%2F57245586%5B%2Furl%5D&h=a2b621f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170923/57245586[/url]</a></span>"},{"pid":"a50623b1abea1b7225facd685c2331509783ca75","tid":411084,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170923/57245586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170923%2F57245586&d=JKh%2BUJ3vdBTNOyz78cyjaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d120e518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170923%2F57245586&h=f24f33ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170923/57245586</a>"},{"pid":"beab8d1f7adf629