隔甩底果個位 無左粒螺絲就要ground得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8235847425f994d8eaccaf619899c7d2c980436","tid":411084,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"岩呀成班港豬見平機票味狗衝囉 真係咪搞我"},{"pid":"2a4f3163bdd3a6cd11157e213fce48602683adb2","tid":411084,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐過因航同港航,frequent flyer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一條route 港航會飛高d慳油,結果climb 同decent rate急好多,進場又會早好多禁低架機,變左好多時都land得唔穩(技術好會岩岩好decent 完就touch down) 。<br />\n<br />\n試過明明天氣無咩特別,但太遲開始decent (一般touch down 前30分鐘或更早已開始decent),結果好rush咁circle 減高度,最後硬食左幾個turbulance (過山車咁,d乘客叫晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDescend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇到我眼花"},{"pid":"802c884258adf0207354bd317ab6252b39510dba","tid":411084,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>差過坐一次港航 <br />\n見到機翼少左粒螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有睇空中浩劫都知<br />\n少左啲螺絲會空中解體<br />\n好唔安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲位係無左粒螺絲先會有機會扯甩塊機皮 例如隔甩底果個位 無左粒螺絲就要ground得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定嗰個位一定係螺絲位？飛機有好多vent hole，我仲記得好junior嗰陣行沙圈見到成排螺絲跟住有個位有個窿，然後同工程師講，佢話嗰個唔係螺絲位，然後叫我去另一邊睇，一樣有個窿"},{"pid":"d2d5e949d3d35edad14703b00a18810ce8e069aa","tid":411084,"uid":59215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>差過坐一次港航 <br />\n見到機翼少左粒螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有睇空中浩劫都知<br />\n少左啲螺絲會空中解體<br />\n好唔安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲位係無左粒螺絲先會有機會扯甩塊機皮 例如隔甩底果個位 無左粒螺絲就要ground得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定嗰個位一定係螺絲位？飛機有好多vent hole，我仲記得好junior嗰陣行沙圈見到成排螺絲跟住有個位有個窿，然後同工程師講，佢話嗰個唔係螺絲位，然後叫我去另一邊睇，一樣有個窿</blockquote><br />\n我知你講邊個位 <br />\n不過做得多你都會記得<br />\n<br />\nBtw 無左粒就要成塊拆 好撚麻煩"},{"pid":"141f63463f4d9f0504cadaff24f3296670ca1519","tid":411084,"uid":59215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquot