"2aa1af3fb10214e6555b3d0f7d659c1b752737ff","tid":411084,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:57:12.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又幫廚叉打飛機<br />\n爽爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09fc33cd351d5188b4e045fec0824e89dac7184","tid":411084,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>差過坐一次港航 <br />\n見到機翼少左粒螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有睇空中浩劫都知<br />\n少左啲螺絲會空中解體<br />\n好唔安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲位係無左粒螺絲先會有機會扯甩塊機皮 例如隔甩底果個位 無左粒螺絲就要ground得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定嗰個位一定係螺絲位？飛機有好多vent hole，我仲記得好junior嗰陣行沙圈見到成排螺絲跟住有個位有個窿，然後同工程師講，佢話嗰個唔係螺絲位，然後叫我去另一邊睇，一樣有個窿</blockquote><br />\n同埋螺絲hole點都會樣衰過 vent hole 日磨夜磨</blockquote><br />\n唔一定，就咁圓型一個窿，佢仲要隔住個mon，佢又會識係螺絲定vent hole...有個老機長教，做呢行你無可能知同做晒所有嘢，信人係其中一樣要習慣接受嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n原來你講梗張相 一定要親眼望先得</blockquote><br />\n就算唔係張相，我行沙圈都捉過幾次真係機身無螺絲或者鬆咗出嚟，有啲連牙都滑埋根本上唔實，咪一樣話照飛，所以好多嘢根本係行外人睇一件事，行內就覺得好正常"},{"pid"